# Content Credentials R Plot Test

This document is a small fixture for testing render/export signing with R plots.
It uses only base R datasets and plotting functions so it does not require extra
R packages.

::: figure

```r exec
plot(
  cars$speed,
  cars$dist,
  pch = 19,
  col = "#2f6f9f",
  xlab = "Speed",
  ylab = "Stopping distance"
)
lines(lowess(cars$speed, cars$dist), col = "#c43d3d", lwd = 2)
```

Stopping distance against speed for the built-in `cars` dataset.

:::

::: figure

```r exec
hist(
  airquality$Temp,
  breaks = 10,
  col = "#7aa35a",
  border = "white",
  xlab = "Temperature",
  main = ""
)
rug(airquality$Temp, col = "#333333")
```

Temperature distribution from the built-in `airquality` dataset.

:::
